== Stash via the Git repository view
	
		(((Eclipse Git,stash via the Git repositories view)))
	
	
		The
		`git stash`
		command is available in the
		__
		_Git repositories_
		view. Right-click on your Git repository and select
		_Stash Changes_
		.
	
	
